design.description: I am a psychologist graduated from the Federal University of Minas Gerais (UFMG). I am currently taking a training course at Instituto C.G. Jung MG, affiliated with the Associação Junguiana do Brasil (AJB) and the International Association for Analytical Psychology (IAAP). I have been working since 2020 in clinical practice as a psychotherapist through the approach of analytical psychology.
